---
// Footer.astro
---

<footer class="mt-auto w-full border-t border-hairline bg-canvas py-8 text-sm distraction">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-(--size-breakpoint-xl) px-6">
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-4">
      <!-- Left side: Standards & Credits -->
      <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-x-4 gap-y-1 text-mute text-xs font-mono">
        <span>The Standard: 1 Word = 5 Keystrokes (including spaces)</span>
      </div>

      <!-- Right side: Quick Info and Toggles -->
      <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-x-6 gap-y-2 text-body text-xs font-sans justify-end">
        <a href="/about" class="hover:text-ink transition-colors cursor-pointer">About Us</a>
        <a href="/privacy" class="hover:text-ink transition-colors cursor-pointer">Privacy Policy</a>
        <a href="/terms" class="hover:text-ink transition-colors cursor-pointer">Terms & Conditions</a>
        <a href="/contact" class="hover:text-ink transition-colors cursor-pointer">Contact Us</a>
        <a href="#rules" class="hover:text-ink transition-colors cursor-pointer" onclick="document.dispatchEvent(new CustomEvent('switch-tab', { detail: { tab: 'stats' } }))">Stats Dashboard</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="mt-6 border-t border-hairline pt-4 flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-between text-[11px] text-mute">
      <span>© 2026 typing speed practice. All rights reserved.</span>
      <span class="mt-1 sm:mt-0">Designed for: Speed, accuracy, and muscle memory.</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
